description:
Family is a shelter, each of the family members is the stanchion of this shelter.it means nobody gets left behind or forgotten.

We as a family support each other in laugh and tears which they faced as the life push them forward, they join by hearth and make the family roof stronger.

This generative artwork inspired from family. The content which shared between many creatures in our plant and one of the nature’s masterpieces.



1600*1600
